00:26:40.836 --> 00:26:42.739
What should I get?

00:26:42.739 --> 00:26:44.471
Whatever.

00:26:45.439 --> 00:26:48.108
- Watch the traffic.
- Got it.

00:26:51.378 --> 00:26:54.348
He says the move date suddenly changed,
so he'll stay at a junior's place.

00:26:54.348 --> 00:26:56.028
Wouldn't that be awkward?

00:26:56.028 --> 00:26:57.188
For who?

00:26:57.188 --> 00:26:58.454
Him?

00:26:58.454 --> 00:27:00.353
Or your feelings?

00:27:01.655 --> 00:27:03.749
