only the lovely sides at this stage.

00:27:56.010 --> 00:27:58.712
You're playing a brinkmanship tactic.

00:27:58.712 --> 00:28:00.380
Right?

00:28:05.152 --> 00:28:06.503
Looks like his junior's here.

00:28:06.503 --> 00:28:08.288
You can get off.

00:28:13.794 --> 00:28:15.864
