00:29:37.945 --> 00:29:39.548
and, um...

00:29:39.548 --> 00:29:41.682
your studio's nearby too.

00:29:41.682 --> 00:29:43.187
Okay.

00:29:43.187 --> 00:29:44.797
I will.

00:29:46.655 --> 00:29:48.388
Really?

00:29:52.405 --> 00:29:54.496
He's my junior.

00:29:54.496 --> 00:29:56.296
Woo Jung Hoon.

00:30:03.927 --> 00:30:04.938
Say hi.

00:30:04.938 --> 00:30:06.742
This is Seo Jun Kyung.

00:30:06.742 --> 00:30:08.142
My girlfriend.

00:30:08.142 --> 00:30:10.012
Oh,

00:30:10.012 --> 00:30:12.012
nice to meet you.

00:30:16.572 --> 00:30:18.385
So,

00:30:18.385 --> 00:30:20.205
you thought

00:30:20.205 --> 00:30:23.056
my junior was a woman?

00:30:29.029 --> 00:30:31.700
What kind of image do I have?

00:30:31.700 --> 00:30:35.835
I'm not that Hollywood.

00:30:36.939 --> 00:30:38.238
It's just...

00:30:38.238 --> 00:30:41.408
No, I mean... his hair looks so silky,

00:30:41.408 --> 00:30:44.944
and his legs are so slim.

00:30:47.706 --> 00:30:50.306
I should treat him to a meal sometime.

00:30:50.306 --> 00:30:52.778
We should eat too.

00:30:53.845 --> 00:30:55.806
Since it's moving day,

00:30:55.806 --> 00:30:58.025
do we have a Chinese place number or something?

00:30:58.025 --> 00:30:59.859
Oh my.

00:31:03.672 --> 00:31:05.598
Thank you.

00:31:07.002 --> 00:31:08.902
For being jealous.

00:31:13.373 --> 00:31:15.608
Hold on a second.

00:31:17.845 --> 00:31:19.446
Hello?

00:31:21.784 --> 00:31:23.686
Oh, I see.

00:31:23.686 --> 00:31:25.785
How close together are the contractions?

00:31:27.588 --> 00:31:29.930
Then, we won't need oxytocin.

00:31:29.930 --> 00:31:31.624
I'll head over now.

00:31:34.863 --> 00:31:36.450
Hey, Sol.

00:31:36.450 --> 00:31:38.350
You said four people, right?

00:31:38.350 --> 00:31:39.910
Five?

00:31:39.910 --> 00:31:42.604
That's fine. Totally fine.

00:31:42.604 --> 00:31:44.505
